# General mechanics; 一般機制
. You will die.; 你會死。
. But don't despair, you will learn something new each time.; 但是不要害怕，你每次都會學到些新東西。
. The aim of Pathos is to survive all the way to level 40 before escaping back at level 1.; Pathos的遊戲目標是活到40層，然後逃回1層。
. Pathos is turn-based so take your time and consider your options when things get serious.; Pathos是回合制的，所以當事情變得麻煩起來的時候你可以慢慢思考該怎麼辦。
. Each class starts with different items, skills and abilities.; 每個職業的初始道具，專精和天賦都不一樣。
. The effects of potions, scrolls, rings, wands and some armour are shuffled at the start of each adventure.; 藥劑、卷軸、戒指和部分防具的效果（外形）會在遊戲開始時隨機設置。這意味著不同遊戲之間的知識並不通用。
. For example, the orange potion will not have a consistent effect across different adventures.; 比如說，橙色藥劑的效果在不同的冒險中會不一樣。

# Combat; 戰鬥
. When attacking a d20 is rolled which gives a random number between 1 and 20.; 當攻擊目標時，會進行一次d20的判定，得到一個1-20之間的隨機數。
. A roll of 1 is a critical miss and a roll of 20 is a critical hit.; 如果投出了1，代表嚴重的失誤，如果投出了20，代表暴擊。
. A critical miss stops any further attacks in that turn (if you have multiple attacks).; 嚴重的失誤會導致本回合內任何接下來的攻擊都不會發生（如果你能攻擊多次）
. A critical hit causes the base weapon damage to be doubled. Note that enchantments and strength modifiers are not doubled.; 暴擊必定命中，會導致武器基礎傷害翻倍。注意附魔和力量屬性修正不會翻倍。
. The strength bonus to damage is doubled when using a two handed weapon.; 當使用雙手武器的時候，力量屬性修正翻倍。使用弓箭時，會額外獲得基於敏捷的修正。
. If a critical is the only way to hit or miss then it is downgraded to a normal hit or miss.; 如果暴擊是唯一能夠命中的方式，此次攻擊會變成普通攻擊（無額外傷害）
. Otherwise, this number is added to the attack score and compared to the defence score.; 否則，這個數字加上你的攻擊會和目標的防禦進行比較。
/
` (Attack + d20) >= Defence; (攻擊 + d20) >= 防禦
/
. Your attack and defence scores are influenced by your abilities, skills and magical enchantments.; 你的攻擊力和防禦力會被你的天賦，專精以及附魔影響。
. Magical enchantments to weapons directly affect your attack score and are also added to the damage score.; 武器附魔直接影響你的攻擊力，以及你造成的傷害值。
/
. Your skill bonus is based on your level and is the same formula for all classes:; 你的等級攻擊力獎勵是基於你的等級，且以下公式適用於所有職業：
/
` Skill Bonus = (Level / 4) + 1; 等級獎勵 = (等級 / 4) + 1
/
. Your defence is also affected by your circumstances:; 你的防禦力會被你的狀態所影響：
/
` {Mod} defence when blind; 當致盲時{Mod} 防禦
` {Mod} defence when invisible; 當隱身時{Mod} 防禦
` {Mod} defence when displaced; 當錯位時{Mod} 防禦
` {Mod} defence when paralysed or sleeping; 當麻痺或者睡眠時{Mod} 防禦
` {Mod} defence when stuck; 當卡住時{Mod} 防禦
` {Mod} defence when punished; 當被懲罰時{Mod} 防禦
` {Mod} defence when attacked from concealment; 當被偷襲時{Mod} 防禦
/
. Heavy armour will make you {UnskilledPenalty} points slower if you are unskilled and {SkilledPenalty} points slower if you are skilled.; 如果你的重甲技能是生疏的，重甲會讓你的速度-{UnskilledPenalty}，如果是熟練以上則改為-{SkilledPenalty}。
. Medium armour is {UnskilledPenalty} point slower if you are unskilled, otherwise no speed adjustment.; 如果你的中甲技能是生疏的，中甲會讓你的速度-{UnskilledPenalty}，如果是熟練以上則改為不受影響。
. Light armour has no speed penalty if you are unskilled.; 輕甲無論何時都不會降低你的速度。
. Unskilled use of armour also attracts a one point defence penalty.; 不擅長的盔甲（技能是生疏的）會讓你的防禦-1。
/
. The dexterity modifier is applied to your defence when you are skilled in all pieces of armour.; 當你穿著所有的防具都是擅長的（技能熟練以上）時，你會獲得敏捷帶來的防禦修正。
. This is limited to a maximum of +4 when wearing any medium armour and +2 when wearing any heavy armour.; 當穿有重甲時，防禦修正值最高為+2；當穿有中甲時，修正值最高為+4。

# Skills; 技能
. Each skill has a rating between 0 and 2000 and there are five competency levels.; 每個技能會有一個-1000到2000的熟練度，如果<0則代表不擅長該技能（生疏）。否則根據熟練度會分為5個等級：
/
` (0) Proficient =    0..199; (0) 熟練     =    0..199
` (1) Specialist =  200..499; (1) 精通     =  200..499
` (2) Expert     =  500..999; (2) 專家     =  500..999
` (3) Master     = 1000..1999; (3) 大師     = 1000..1999
` (4) Champion   = 2000; (4) 冠軍     = 2000
/
. Skill ratings are improved with practice such as hitting with a weapon and not being hit wearing armour.; 技能熟練度是通過技能來提升的，比如拿著武器打人或者穿著盔甲被打。
/
. Weapon skill gives you the competency level as an attack bonus and to damage.; 武器技能會為你的攻擊帶來額外的攻擊力加成和傷害加成。
. For example, a master in heavy blade receives +3 attack and +3 damage when using a two handed sword.; 比如說，大師級重刃技能會在你使用雙手劍的時候給你帶來+3攻擊力和+3傷害的獎勵。
. This bonus to damage is doubled on a critical hit.; 這個傷害獎勵在暴擊時會翻倍。
/
. Armour skill gives you the competency level as a defence bonus.; 防具技能會給你帶來額外的防禦加成。
. For example, an expert in heavy armour receives +2 defence when wearing plate mail.; 比如說，專家級重甲技能會在你穿著板甲的時候給你帶來+2防禦力獎勵。
. The defence bonus is the average of the skill levels on each piece of equipped armour.; 防禦獎勵由身上所有的裝備的平均技能等級決定。
. For example, an expert (2) in heavy armour whom is only proficient (0) in light armour is wearing plate mail (heavy) and a small shield (light) so would have a defence bonus of +1.; 比如說，你的重甲技能是專家級（2點獎勵），但你的輕甲是熟練級（0點獎勵），且你裝備了一個板甲（重甲）和一個小盾（輕甲），那麼你得到的防禦獎勵是+1。
/
. Skill in schools of magic improves the casting range and has better effects at each competency level.; 魔法類的技能會給你帶來施法距離和施法效果的提升。
. These skills are practised by learning and casting spells.; 這些技能通過學習法術和釋放法術來提升。.

# Life; 生命值
. {LifeDefinition};{LifeDefinition}
. Your starting life is determined by your race and class plus your constitution modifier.;您的初始生命值由兩部分相加而成，種族和職業決定的基礎數值，和您的體質修正值。
. When you advance an experience level, your life is increased by a random amount determined by your race and class plus your constitution modifier.;當您升級之後，您的最大生命值會產生變化，變化數值是隨機的，其值為種族、職業決定的基礎數值與體質修正值之和。
. There are also magical means to increase your life potential.;您可以通過一些神奇的方法增加自己的基礎生命值。
. However, life cannot be increased past the maximum potential plus your constitution score.;但是，您的最大生命值不能超過基礎生命值上限與您體質之和。
/
` Initial = Class base + Race base + {CON} modifier;初始生命值 = 職業基礎數值 + 種族基礎數值 + {CON} 修正值
` Advancement = Class roll + Race roll + {CON} modifier;升級獲得最大生命值 = 職業決定的隨機數 + 種族決定的隨機數 + {CON} 修正值
` Limit = Initial + max(Advancement) x Level + {CON} score;最大生命值上限 = 初始生命值 +  通過升級獲得的生命值中的最大值 x 等級 + {CON} 修正值
/
. Life naturally recovers at one point per ({LevelCap} - Level - {CON} modifier) turns.;生命值每過({LevelCap} - 等級 - {CON} 修正值)個回合可以自動回復一點。
. Sleeping improves recovery by halving the number of turns.;睡覺可以讓自動回復所需的回合數減半，從而加快恢復。
. Starvation causes life to recover at one point per {StarvationRecoveryRate} turns.;極度飢餓會使您每過{StarvationRecoveryRate}個回合損失一點生命值。
. Life regeneration guarantees the recovery at one point per turn.;生命恢復天賦可以使您每回合回復一點生命。
. The {inediate} diet slows recovery of life by doubling the number of turns.;{inediate}食物會讓自動回復所需的回合數翻倍，從而減慢恢復。
. When the {hunger} property is present in combination with the {inediate} diet, life will no longer naturally recover. However, with the addition of {life regeneration}, life will recover at the usual slower rate.;當一個{inediate}食性的角色擁有{hunger}狀態或天賦時，生命值將不再自動回復。但是如果你有{life regeneration}天賦或狀態時，生命回復會和正常情況一樣緩慢增長
. Active {phasing} prevents the natural recovery of life.;激活{phasing}時會抑制生命值的自然回復。

